title: People's Court: The Mud Room vs Dirty Socks
description: We have a people's court with Falen and Jake where they both plead their cases.  Falen argues that Jake doesn't use the mud room that he wanted so bad in their new house and Jake argues Falen is disgusting because she leaves dirty socks everywhere.  We have listeners on to decide who wins their case.
